=== Testing Supabase .single() mock structure ===

Current test scripts:
  test:safe: vitest --run --maxConcurrency=1 --poolOptions.threads.maxThreads=1
  test:services: vitest --run src/app/services/__tests__/ src/services/__tests__/
  test:full: NODE_OPTIONS='--max-old-space-size=4096' vitest --run --isolate=true --maxConcurrency=6 --poolOptions.threads.maxThreads=6 --poolOptions.threads.singleThread=false

--run flag presence:
  test:safe: ✓ Present
  test:services: ✓ Present
  test:full: ✓ Present

=== Expected Mock Chain Structure ===
After fixes, Supabase mocks should support:
  - from().select().eq().single() → { data, error }
  - from().insert().select().single() → { data, error }
  - from().select().eq().gt().single() → { data, error }
  - from().update().eq().single() → { data, error }
All chainable methods must return objects with next method in chain

stdout | src/app/__tests__/bugfix/test-failures-fix.exploration.test.ts > Test Failures Fix - Bug Condition Exploration > should document expected behavior after fixes are applied

=== EXPECTED BEHAVIOR AFTER FIXES ===

1. Test Suite Completion:
   - npm run test:safe completes in under 3 minutes 20 seconds
   - npm run test:services completes in under 60 seconds
   - npm run test:full completes in under 3 minutes 20 seconds
   - All test commands exit with code 0 (pass) or 1 (fail)
   - No manual Ctrl+C required to terminate processes

2. Supabase Mock Chaining:
   - All service tests using .single() pass without errors
   - Mock chains return proper { data, error } structure
   - No "Cannot read property 'single' of undefined" errors
   - No "TypeError: mockChain.single is not a function" errors

3. Preservation Requirements:
   - Individual test execution continues to work (e.g., npm run test:button)
   - Watch mode scripts continue to work (e.g., npm run test:watch)
   - All 74 currently passing service tests continue to pass
   - Component tests continue to pass with existing mocks
   - Test configuration settings remain unchanged

=== ROOT CAUSES IDENTIFIED ===

Root Cause 1: Missing --run flag in test scripts
  - vitest run command without --run flag may enter watch mode
  - Watch mode waits indefinitely for file changes
  - Process never exits, blocking automated workflows
  - Fix: Add --run flag to test:safe, test:full, test:services scripts

Root Cause 2: Incomplete mock chain for .single() method
  - Service test mocks properly chain from(), select(), eq()
  - But some query chains fail when .single() is called
  - Mock structure must exactly match query builder API shape
  - Fix: Ensure all chainable methods return objects with .single() method

